content:
Can you provide information on the top five animal species found in the Amazon rainforest and also share two interesting facts about the rainforest?
Here is some Swift code to display information on the animal species:
let animalSpecies = ["Jaguar", "Anaconda", "Harpy Eagle", "Poison Dart Frog", "Sloth"]
for animal in animalSpecies {
    print("The \(animal) is one of the top five animal species found in the Amazon rainforest.")
}
